<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .order-details { background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 0; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ“¦ New Order Received</h1>
      <p><strong>System Notification</strong></p>
    </div>

    <p>Hello Admin Team,</p>
    
    <p>A new order has been successfully created and requires your attention.</p>

    <div class="order-details">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1f2937;">Order Overview</h2>
      
      <p><strong>Client Company:</strong> <%= @order.client.company_name %></p>
      <p><strong>Contact Person:</strong> <%= @order.client.personal_name %></p>
      <p><strong>Ordered by:</strong> <%= @order.ordered_by&.email || "Unknown User" %></p>
      <p><strong>Project Reference:</strong> <%= @order.project&.name || 'Not specified' %></p>
      <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %H:%M") %></p>
      <p><strong>Delivery Date:</strong> <%= @order.delivery_date ? @order.delivery_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") : 'Not specified' %></p>
      <p><strong>Total Quantity:</strong> <%= number_with_delimiter(@order.total_quantity) %> units</p>
      <p><strong>Total Value:</strong> $<%= number_with_delimiter(@order.price) %></p>
    </div>

    <h3>Order Items Summary:</h3>
    <ul>
      <% @order.order_items.each do |item| %>
        <li>
          <strong><%= item.product.name %></strong> - 
          Qty: <%= item.quantity %> | 
          Color: <%= item.color.presence || 'N/A' %> | 
          Size: <%= item.size.presence || 'Standard' %>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= admin_order_url(@order) %>" class="button">
        ðŸ‘€ Review Full Order Details
      </a>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> Please review the order details and proceed with processing according to standard operating procedures.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated notification from the <%= Rails.application.class.module_parent_name %> Order Management System.</p>
      <p>Generated on: <%= Time.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %H:%M %Z") %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>